ticketedEvent.description:
We’re taking over an intimate venue in North Beach for a night of laugh-until-you-cry comedy - featuring talent you’ve seen on Netflix, Comedy Central and HBO.

Must be 21+ to attend 
Ticket sales are final, there are no refunds
ticketedEvent.name: The Setup Underground Comedy Show
ticketedEvent.supportString: If you have any support questions, please contact The Setup at info@setupcomedy.com.
